38:47.880 --> 38:49.140
Sini, ulurkan tangan.

38:51.280 --> 38:53.230
Semoga perintisan usaha kita lancar.

38:53.230 --> 38:54.800
Semoga semua lancar!

38:57.630 --> 38:58.690
Oh ya, Kak Xiaolan,

38:58.710 --> 38:59.880
