41:41.920 --> 41:43.780
Aku lihat dia tampak cukup ramah.

41:44.280 --> 41:45.920
Hubungan manusia itu
dibangun seiring berjalannya waktu.

41:45.920 --> 41:46.510
Kita

41:46.670 --> 41:48.470
